 U^{\dagger } \overset{\rightharpoonup }{\sigma } U
\overset{\rightharpoonup }{\sigma }=\sigma _x \overset{\rightharpoonup }{x}+\overset{\rightharpoonup }{y} \sigma _z+\sigma _z \overset{\rightharpoonup }{z}
U = e^{i t \omega  \sigma _z}
 U^{\dagger } \sigma _x U  =   \underset{n}{\Sigma } e_n U^{\dagger } |n'\rangle \langle n'| U=\underset{n}{\Sigma } e_n   |n'\rangle \langle n'|
U^{\dagger } \overset{\rightharpoonup }{\sigma } U
 {\rm U}\left(t\right) \equiv \exp\left({\rm i}\,\omega t\,\sigma_{z}\right) 
\ddot{\rm U}\left(t\right) + \omega^{2}{\rm U}\left(t\right) = 0
{\rm U}\left(0\right) = 1
\dot{{\rm U}}\left(0\right) = {\rm i}\omega\sigma_{z}
A\left(t\right) \equiv {\rm U}^{\dagger}\left(t\right)A{\rm U}\left(t\right)
{\rm i}\dot{A} = \omega\left[\sigma_{z},A\left(t\right)\right]
 {\rm i}\dot{\sigma}_{x}\left(t\right) = \omega\left[{\rm i}\sigma_{y}\left(t\right)\right]\,, \qquad {\rm i}\dot{\sigma}_{y}\left(t\right) = \omega\left[-{\rm i}\sigma_{x}\left(t\right)\right]\,; \qquad {{\rm d}\left[\sigma_{x}\left(t\right) + {\rm i}\sigma_{y}\left(t\right)\right]  \over  {\rm d}t} = -{\rm i}\omega \left[\sigma_{x}\left(t\right) + {\rm i}\sigma_{y}\left(t\right)\right] 
 \sigma_{x}\left(t\right) = \sigma_{x}\cos\left(\omega t\right) + \sigma_{y}\sin\left(\omega t\right)\,, \qquad \sigma_{y}\left(t\right) = -\sigma_{x}\sin\left(\omega t\right) + \sigma_{y}\cos\left(\omega t\right) 
